videos.headline: 1-seed Gamecocks offense overwhelms 8-seed Arkansas
videos.description: South Carolina secures a spot in the SEC Tournament semifinals with a 93-66 victory over the Razorbacks led by Aliyah Boston, Victaria Saxton, and Laeticia Amihere.
